-- India gives BlackBerry August 31 deadline on services
-- 
-- Thu Aug 12, 2010 8:30am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/08/12/us-blackberry-deadline-idUSTRE67B29S20100812

 

 NEW DELHI  (Reuters) - India has given Research In Motion until Aug 31 to address the government's security concerns over its BlackBerry service, a government source said on Thursday. 

